This prestigious brand new 3 bedroom, plus study home offers the very best for families. Designed with elegance and style in mind, this home is sure to impress. Positioned in the prime Livingstone Estate, it provides a modern, active and convenient way of life in a secure and friendly environment.
Featuring:
- Three bedrooms, master with ensuite and walk in robe
- Open plan study

Description:
Elegance is an understatement
Directions to get to the property:
- Enter Casey Fields via Casey Fields Boulevard off Berwick – Cranbourne Rd
- At the 3rd Roundabout turn Right onto Lineham Drive
- Take 1st Left onto Brittle Gum Road
- Take 3rd Left onto Stark Circuit
- Third house on the right is 51 Stark Circuit
Link to find the address online: https://her.is/2k3YuR1
Located in the much sought after Parks Edge Estate, this gorgeous custom Porter Davis built home is certain to surpass all expectations! Properties like this are a true rarity. This home oozes pure elegance, luxury and style and has been built to the highest level of quality and standards.
The home begins with an extra-large doorway that's sure to impress upon entry. The floor plan begins with a large master suite, which includes a 3 door robe, WIR, ensuite with double vanities and an oversized shower with dual shower heads and a seat! The home also has two large living spaces, including a fully enclosed theatre/rumpus room.
But if that doesn't impress you, then the kitchen in this home most certainly will, with stone bench tops, 900mm oven, dishwasher, mirror splash back, soft closing cupboards/drawers, walk in pantry with fridge recess, double under-mount sink ,capped cold water point, built in rubbish bin, dedicated spice drawers - just to name a few! With a kitchen like this, you couldn't ask for more!
Some of the added premium extras in this home include:
- Bamboo Flooring
- High ceilings
- Downlights
- Reverse Cycle Split System (Smart Home Device/Operated by App)
- Stone bench tops throughout - kitchen, pantry, laundry, bathroom and ensuite
- Illume skylights
- Roller shutters to the entirety of the home
- Crimsafe security screens
- Travertine natural stone pillars
- Reticulated gardens (Smart Home Device/Operated by App)
- Exposed aggregate
- Stacker door & Water feature
- Plumbed natural gas point to entertaining area
- Ducted heating
- Soft closing cupboards/drawers
- Build in Robes to all bedrooms
Not only does this gorgeous home offer ample living space, and storage capacity but it also offers great location. Short proximity to Casey Fields, Casey Grammar School, Cranbourne East Primary and Secondary School, Chisholm Tafe Cranbourne, Casey Race, Hunt Club Shopping Centre and Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre.
Don't miss this great opportunity; call Naval Singh or Irene Baselyous for more information!

SOLD by Gavin Coyne 0417 309 650
If you have been looking for your dream home, a place where you can simply move in, unpack and relax then an inspection is a must! Ideally suited to those requiring multiple living zones this fine example of family living is perfectly located in a prime position of Cascades on Clyde Estate, close to Selandra Rise and Hunt Club Shopping Centres, local schools, public transport and beautiful parkland and walking tracks.
Featuring four bedrooms, the master with full en-suite and walk-in robe and the other three bedrooms have built-in robes and are serviced by the main bathroom. A great family home with everything at your fingertips!

Description:
ROOM FOR A POOL, BOATS AND CARAVAN
CRANBOURNE EAST-CASCADES ON CLYDE
This attractive looking home is in the right place for alot of the up and coming amenities in sought after Cascades on Clyde Estate.
On a generous block placed a short stroll from popular parks, shops (Woolworths and several other specialty shops, this beautifully proportioned home offers a lifestyle of convenience and quietude.
The house offers four generous sized bedrooms, a formal lounge, open plan kitchen, dining area, family room, practical laundry, two bathrooms and two toilets.
The master bedroom has a walk in robe and ensuite is sleek and modern. The other three bedrooms have built in robes. The floor plan cleverly places a distance between the parents and kids. The other robed bedrooms are positioned off the hallway to ensure sound sleep for little ones as you go about your day.
One of the other great attributes is that the home has a good size backyard with plenty of room to add in a swimming pool, to have large pets or kids running around playing ball games. Good size double garage with remote and rear access.
Gorgeous area with also a great bonus comes with energy efficient led lights, ducted heating and cooling.
Should definitely fancy an investor that wants sound residents or a buyer that wants to be close to everything imaginable.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short
drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away
from freeway access en route to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, the recently
constructed Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the town centre. Not to
mention just seconds away from the newly developed Selandra rise and Hunt Club village shopping
centres.

Description:
**SOLD BY PAUL RINGERI**
PARKS EDGE ESTATE, CRANBOURNE EAST: Only app. 4 years young and in better than new condition, this gem is positioned in the blossoming Parks Edge estate and is perfectly suited to first home buyers, investors and empty nesters looking to downscale. The property itself is nestled on a care free block allowing you to spend more time enjoying the house and less time maintaining it. With impressive landscaping and display quality presentation you can literally move in, unpack and relax!
Inside, the light tones, gloss tiles and colourful presentation make you feel instantly at home. The functional floorplan includes an open plan living/dining area and a galley style kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher and a large walk in pantry. There are 3 robed bedrooms, including the master with a walk-in wardrobe and a full ensuite, plus an additional family bathroom that easily services the remaining 2 bedrooms. Don't forget the generous study nook, or bonus sitting area, as well as extras including ducted heating, split system air- conditioning and a video intercom.
Step outside to find a double garage with a remote door and internal access together with a compact backyard offering a decked alfresco ideal for relaxing and entertaining.
Within a short drive to freeway access and all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne this sensational opportunity is only minutes away from the popular Clyde Primary School, One Early Education Group offering long day care and kindergarten facilities, Casey RACE Recreation & Aquatic Centre and Casey Indoor Sports Centre! With additional shopping precincts in Pasadena, Selandra Rise/Cascades on Clyde and The Hunt Club local amenities are always going to be close by, whilst the recently revamped Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre offers an abundance of cafes and restaurants! Don't forget the proposed Cranbourne East train station, or the existing ones situated right throughout the South East!
If you want your family to have easy access to the very best in entertainment, education and recreation then call today before it's SELLING, SELLING ..... SOLD!

Grow Estate is right in the heart of all the action in this rapidly expanding area of Melbourne's South East. Description:
SOLD BY BRANDON WHITTA!
Cranbourne East: Located in the popular Cascades on Clyde estate sits this astonishing 4 bedroom
plus study Porter Davis delight! Boasting an enormous 578m2 block, this home ticks all the boxes
and more!
Upon entry you will be immediately blown away by the quality on display, with a keen eye for
detail this home will be sure to impress even the pickiest of buyers. The huge master comes
complete with his and hers walk in robes, massive full en suite with dual vanities and extended
shower space.
The hostess kitchen is a chef's dream and is complete with quality stainless steel appliances
including a dishwasher, 900mm range hood, 5-burner gas cook top, caesar stone bench tops, glass
splash back, ample overhead storage and bench space. Not to mention your very own walk in pantry
fitted with an abundance of shelf space. All of this overlooking your separate meals and living zone.
Not only is this home fitted out with top quality fixtures and fittings it also presents a grand capacity
to accommodate even the largest of families, this is truly an entertainers delight with multiple living
zones on offer!
Added features include: down lights throughout, high ceilings, ducted heating & evaporative cooling,
plantation shutters, velocity fibre optic internet connection, widened exposed aggregate driveway plus much more!
As you step through your timber bi-folding doors you will be instantly greeted by an immaculate
outdoor entertaining area, with both an alfresco fitted with custom feature walls, water features
and a decked pergola area. Not to mention the perfectly manicured landscaping in the front and rear
yard, you will start to understand just how special this family home is!
Surrounded by top end properties and is within walking distance to picturesque wetlands, this home
boasts convenience. Other estate features include Class- A recycled water ensuring lush gardens
year round, over 14 hectares of parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities, playgrounds
and walking tracks.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short
drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away
from freeway access en route to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, the recently
constructed Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the town centre. Not to
mention just seconds away from the newly developed Selandra rise and Hunt Club village shopping
centres.
From front to back this home was completed with an exceptional eye for detail and will be the
perfect residence for those that expect nothing but the best!

Nestled in a fantastic pocket in the new & popular Parks Edge Estate, this modern four bedroom home offers generous living space as well as a convenient lifestyle. On approximately 448m2, there is literally nothing to do but move in and enjoy the low maintenance landscaped gardens and contemporary design.
Features include:
- Large light filled Master bedroom with his & hers walk through robes as well as its own full ensuite featuring twin vanities
- A further three generously sized bedrooms all with double built in robes
- Luxurious open plan living area including dining and family space

- Outdoor alfresco area – perfect to kick back with a glass of wine and entertain guests

- Other features include: Ducted heating throughout, evaporative cooling & NBN access
Conveniently located in Cranbourne East close to Casey Fields and bus services, easy access to schools such as Cranbourne East Secondary College. The perfect choice for those looking for an easy, low maintenance lifestyle!
